name.value: Integration Flow for Harvesting Twitter Data

body.value:
Hello User,

You have received a notification mail from Twitter Data Harvesting iFlow.

You have not configured the predefined subject or search term for the Twitter channel in the Social Intelligence system.

Hello User,

You have received a notification mail from Twitter Data Harvesting iFlow.

There is an error while uploading the data through Social Intelligence Generic OData Interface.
